              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>Conclusions</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>1. States with weak law coverage consistently dominate the top firearm homicide rankings.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='10'>2. Individual states rarely show an immediate drop after new legislation, but the national average shows a long term downward trend.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
